        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是我测试代码高亮的一篇文章。</p><pre><code class="language-python">class Solution:    def twoSum(self, nums: List[int], target: int) -&gt; List[int]:        hashmap = {}        for i, num in enumerate(nums):            if target - num in hashmap:                return [hashmap[target - num], i]            hashmap[num] = i        return []</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
